measurements.description: One hundred twenty-four stellate white flowers and 18 buds on 15 arching to pendant up to 16-cm inflorescences; plant 21-cm wide by 31-cm tall, mounted on 14-cm wide by 27-cm tall cork slab; sepals lanceolate, slightly reflexed apically ; petals acuminate, slightly reflexed apically; lip trilobed, midlobe narrowly acute, side lobe margins denticulate, spur 4.0-cm long; anther cap yellow; substance firm; texture crystalline; citrus fragrance noted, plant nearly obscured by inflorescences, natural spread vertical includes spur, also received award 20255296.
